<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-05 14:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4196 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-BELGRADE-2TAKE     06-05 0892
