<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;    ONCE THE BOMBS STOP, REBUILDING KOSOVO WILL BE SLOW, DIFFICULT
AND COSTLY
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
